descript.abstract: This polygon data layer represents land use for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2005. [Parcel based land use inventory for Dane County for the year 2005.]
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This data set was developed for site specific and regional planning including land use, transportation and environmental resource applications.]
descript.supplinf: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement where applicable. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://www.countyofdane.com/lio/datacatalog.aspx.
